description.narrative: Regional Action Through Data (RAD) will improve health and development outcomes in sub-Saharan Africa by changing how and why data is collected and analyzed to achieve results. Activities include (1) regional level: equip and empower stakeholders with evidence-based analytics to drive policy, strategy, program development, and resource allocation; (2) patient/provider level: focus on cross-border populations by implementing a cloud-based personal electronic health record system, integrating cross-border data collection to ensure quality and continuity of patient care regardless of their location.
